powerpc: Define/use HUGETLB_NEED_PRELOAD insead of complicated #if

Define HUGETLB_NEED_PRELOAD in mmu-book3e.h for CONFIG_PPC64 instead
of having a much more complicated #if block.  This is easier to read
and maintain.

